opy = 35046</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.BufferUsageHint.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The static copy buffer usage hint</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DynamicDraw = 35048</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.BufferUsageHint.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The dynamic draw buffer usage hint</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DynamicRead = 35049</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.BufferUsageHint.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The dynamic read buffer usage hint</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DynamicCopy = 35050</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.BufferUsageHint.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The dynamic copy buffer usage hint</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
